reviews.review_text:
Great source Allow me to be the first to say this source is indeed "fan-fking-tastic!"

Sound quality and separation are excellent. Pig's organ isn't buried in the mix, Bobby is clearly mixed, and the performance is worthy of being the Dead's last show at the Fillmore West. 

Check out the Hard to Handle and Other One. The whole night is solid though. 

Thanks for this beautiful upgrade!

dig that bass line Phil, you're so hard to handle, now mess around. 

Superb reverb bass resonance and acoustic integrity, even after all these years.
